```plantuml
@startuml laziestcoder_Budget_App_JS

actor User
participant "UI (HTML/CSS)" as UI
participant "Controller" as Controller
participant "UIController" as UIController
participant "BudgetController" as BudgetController

User -> UI: Inputs income/expense data
UI -> Controller: Triggers event (click/add)
Controller -> UIController: getInput()
UIController --> Controller: Returns input data

Controller -> BudgetController: addItem(type, desc, val)
BudgetController -> BudgetController: Stores item\nCalculates budget\nUpdates percentages
BudgetController --> Controller: Returns updated data

Controller -> UIController: addListItem(item, type)
UIController -> UI: Updates DOM with new item

Controller -> UIController: updateBudget()
UIController -> UI: Displays updated totals\nand percentages

@enduml
```